{"title":"Samba快速入门","uid":"d5477574fa77bf54e6e43f047273c678","slug":"Samba快速入门","date":"2018-01-21T10:11:41.000Z","updated":"2022-10-19T10:08:40.339Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Samba快速入门.json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://gimg2.baidu.com/image_search/src=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.linux.net.cn%2Fdata%2Fattachment%2Falbum%2F201604%2F19%2F062345dr9dg55vw3ul7ovk.jpg&refer=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.linux.net.cn&app=2002&size=f9999,10000&q=a80&n=0&g=0n&fmt=auto?sec=1668765999&t=c784db0c712b26ee7a2ea1ca9adcfecd","content":"<h3 id=\"安装Samba\"><a href=\"#安装Samba\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"安装Samba\"></a>安装Samba</h3><pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">[root@localhost ~]# yum install samba -y\n[root@localhost ~]# cd &#x2F;etc&#x2F;samba&#x2F;\n[root@localhost samba]# ls\nlmhosts  smb.conf  smb.conf.example\n[root@localhost samba]# mv smb.conf smb.conf.bak\n[root@localhost samba]# grep -v &quot;#&quot; smb.conf.bak &gt; smb.conf \n</code></pre>\n<h3 id=\"配置文件smb-conf\"><a href=\"#配置文件smb-conf\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"配置文件smb.conf\"></a>配置文件smb.conf</h3><pre class=\"line-numbers language-conf\" data-language=\"conf\"><code class=\"language-conf\">[root@localhost samba]# vim smb.conf\n\n[global]\n        workgroup &#x3D; SAMBA\n        security &#x3D; user \n\n        passdb backend &#x3D; tdbsam\n\n        printing &#x3D; cups\n        printcap name &#x3D; cups\n        load printers &#x3D; yes\n        cups options &#x3D; raw\n[myshare]\n                ##共享文件目录路径\n                path&#x3D;&#x2F;opt&#x2F;wbm         \n                browseable&#x3D;yes\n                create mask&#x3D;0644\n                directory mask&#x3D;0755\n                ##允许访问的用户\n                valid users&#x3D;wbm\n                ##允许写入的用户\n                write list&#x3D;wbm  </code></pre>\n<h3 id=\"创建用户\"><a href=\"#创建用户\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"创建用户\"></a>创建用户</h3><pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">[root@localhost samba]#useradd wbm</code></pre>\n<h3 id=\"给用户设置密码\"><a href=\"#给用户设置密码\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"给用户设置密码\"></a>给用户设置密码</h3><pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">[root@localhost samba]#smbpasswd -a wbm </code></pre>\n<h3 id=\"列出smb用户列表\"><a href=\"#列出smb用户列表\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"列出smb用户列表\"></a>列出smb用户列表</h3><pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">[root@localhost samba]#pdbedit -L  \nwbm:1000:</code></pre>\n<h3 id=\"创建Samba共享目录\"><a href=\"#创建Samba共享目录\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"创建Samba共享目录\"></a>创建Samba共享目录</h3><pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">[root@localhost ~]#mkdir &#x2F;opt&#x2F;wbm\n[root@localhost ~]#chmod 777 &#x2F;opt&#x2F;wbm\n[root@localhost ~]#systemctl start smb.service </code></pre>\n<h3 id=\"挂在samba共享\"><a href=\"#挂在samba共享\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"挂在samba共享\"></a>挂在samba共享</h3><pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">[root@vm22 ~]# mount -t cifs &#x2F;&#x2F;192.168.10.21&#x2F;wbm &#x2F;opt&#x2F;wbm&#x2F; -o username&#x3D;wbm,password&#x3D;qwer1.2.3.\n[root@vm22 ~]# cd &#x2F;opt&#x2F;wbm&#x2F;\n[root@vm22 wbm]# ls\nInstall_nginx.sh</code></pre>\n<h3 id=\"开机自动挂载\"><a href=\"#开机自动挂载\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"开机自动挂载\"></a>开机自动挂载</h3><pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">[root@vm22 wbm]# vim &#x2F;etc&#x2F;fstab\n\n#在末尾处添加\n\n&#x2F;&#x2F;192.168.10.21 &#x2F;opt&#x2F;wbm    cifs username&#x3D;wbm,password&#x3D;qwer1.2.3. 0 0</code></pre>","feature":true,"text":"安装Samba[root@localhost ~]# yum install samba -y [root@localhost ~]# cd &#x2F;etc&#x2F;samba&#x2F; [root@localhost samba]# ls lmhosts smb.con...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"1.6k","symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categori